{"type": "article", "id": 43623, "title": "Prada 出了胶囊系列，以及，你能通过这些单品回顾嘻哈时尚 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-08-01T03:02:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 2267, "name": "Longchamp"}, {"id": 6149, "name": "hip-hop"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 10762, "name": "Kappa"}, {"id": 39155, "name": "Fear of God"}, {"id": 3113, "name": "Salvatore Ferragamo"}, {"id": 9692, "name": "BCBG MAX AZRIA"}, {"id": 23148, "name": "花王"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170801104726BcHZuzGFrjliIXd6.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/454666\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>日本日化巨头花王发布半年财报，净利润上涨 12.4%</strong></a> | 截止至今年 6 月 30 日的六个月间，花王的销售额同比上涨了 2.5%，至 7173 亿日元，净利润上涨了 12.4%，至 569 亿日元。其中，受入境消费减少的影响，护肤品和护发用品的销售略有下降，但健康辅助类产品获得了 9.9%的增长。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/salvatore-ferragamo-net-profit-down-15-4-in-first-half-10954474/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Salvatore Ferragamo 发布半年财报，净利润跌了 15.4%</strong></a> | 截止至 6 月 30 日，Salvatore Ferragamo 的半年净利润跌了 15.4%，至 7600 万欧元，营收上涨了 1.1％ 至 7.18 亿欧元。截至目前，该品牌共有 679 个销售点，包括 401 家直营店和 278 家第三方经营门店，亚太地区是最主要的市场，贡献了 37.8% 的销售额。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/marquee-brands-acquires-bcbg-max-azria-for-108-million\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>美国时装品牌 BCBG MAX Azria 被收购</strong></a> | 美国品牌管理公司 Marquee Brands 以 1.08 亿美元收购 BCBG MAX Azria Global Holdings。这家公司之前还收购了美国水上运动品牌 Body Glove、意大利鞋履品牌 Bruno Magli 等品牌。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>携手由仓石一树和 Lucas Price 主理的品牌 A.FOUR LABS，以及哥本哈根实验音乐厂牌 Posh Isolation，<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/a-four-labs-x-posh-isolation-x-kappa-2017-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kappa 推出了 2017 秋冬三方跨界联名系列</a>。该系列包括 T-shirt、卫衣、球鞋以及 Kappa 经典运动套装在内的 11 件单品，将于 8 月 5 号在 Kappa 官方线上店铺正式发售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103640wRH4z2LVeC3Ad0yk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103640ArNuZxXYUJi3vqfa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103640IYWiceVu1QZ7Aawy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103641WM7sULQVkC41hSlD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103641bSXU0EGYN4WLpjkc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708011036416wmD4EqTOA9VQfsC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103642ZUrKmeq4XlWvhgaE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103642EkfSHoFUzdAiux70.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103642xFZC9fW7QVnPTOcm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103642RO8cPnQEi2HAut6d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103642EfJ0up6TogsiaUSc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103643iUWITwekRGHEhqdr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-08-01/prada-postergirl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada 推出了一个名为 Poster Girl 的胶囊系列</a>，包括毛衫和 T 恤等单品，将在 8 月正式发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103707fZ574vA8aOlMDN0W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.462500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708011037074SrwMauGZgeXoNlh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498485\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103707bxSQ3KkDNlvzWh5L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498485\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103706xZcR52wtWU178Msu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103706sUObnfNYoLT26ix4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103706M6umSdPX378RTNVE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708011037062ExHJcSVKTfdRmD3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103706QpEt4fvL10xhUBCZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103707e2wnaqSXotrv7TsB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103713m01btVBXPjk6O5K9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/fear-of-god-x-vans-2017-teaser\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Fear of God x Vans 2017 全新联名系列公开</a>，这次双方一共带来了 Era，Slip-On 和 Half Cab 三款鞋型，来看看：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103740YDhrzJIOHlS0fQki.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666376\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103744so9F4fCg6NpIhc8n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708011037402VAhEgxQYHRmiG4X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103740iQHwTSPgV0t2b45u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666379\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708011037500Ib1MpT7PY5JOFGx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103750cwFiMAKJ9U8tbBux.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>丹麦超模<a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/handbags/longchamp-freja-beha-erichsen/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Freja Beha Erichsen 为 Longchamp 演绎了 2017 秋冬系列大片</a>，全新推出的 Mademoiselle Longchamp 手袋系列凭借着经典复古的网孔设计，极为抢眼。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103840vK3qP7xOwesgcoDr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103838LVbi03lMDnd9cjEN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103837cQ6rkbPTa32l8njO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708011038391OVKFXwiqjgxRSZW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103837jC5W2ZdKMvFc91Qr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103839U89cHQbjGxg25Csk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103839LjAMBo621CT54tID.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103837Y8no6vyhBZLdEXeQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103837KrUceT5G8fMOsk1g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103838uyGETJ9qF2NgrMml.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708011038382FbpETKAytS1xqJg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103844IGACk7OQP3YDxJlq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103844hmCAVZq60ibcjGyB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>上世纪 80、90 年代被认为是 Hip-Hop 的黄金年代，那个时期诞生了独特的嘻哈时尚潮流。近 30 年之后，日本杂志 Mastered 总结了<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/07/28/hip-hop-90s-fashion-culture/\" rel=\"nofollow\">嘻哈时尚的代表单品</a>，来看看都有哪些： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801103955p9gwfRTF3kb2vYLX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801104006mu4HnbNg3RMwaZF7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801104007GrNVIwSPjDg27ufB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801104007xqZEO9tshbv8jgFp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801104007iEAd4kgFnm7Vztqf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801104007PiNYtsv3mE4ofyju.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801104007vBQdTfMe9iYyDJub.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </